  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: Long sum 0.12345678912345678 ETH is sent.\r\nIn 1-1 chat there is only 0.123456789 shown and ETH is hidden behind right edge\r\n![chat and long sum](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6584810/24300056/71cbc058-10ab-11e7-9c39-2d0b11a65039.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nThe complete sum and currency are visible and do not overlap other ui elements \r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\n1. In Transactions sum overlaps Address and Date\r\n2. In 1-1 chat there is only 0.123456789 shown instead of 0.12345678912345678 and ETH is hidden behind right edge\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status and login\r\n- In 1-1 chat send someone 0.12345678912345678 ETH\r\n- Open Wallet to see Transactions\r\n- Open 1-1 chat to see the sent sum and currency\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.4\r\n* Operating System: Android (Samsung Galaxy S6) and iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
